Interface ClientDataStore<T,S extends Edit<? extends Diff>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the Document that this data store can handle.
    S - The type of Edits that this synchronizer can handle

    public interface ClientDataStore<T,S extends Edit<? extends Diff>>
extends DataStore<T,S>
    A client side DataStore implementation is responsible for storing and serving data for a Differential Synchronization implementation.
